         Kondom.Des.Grauens.1996.GERMAN.1080P.BLURAY.AVC-UNDERTAKERS


         The plot takes place in New York, and in the present.
         In a Hotel called "Quicky" a professor blackmails a
         student of his into having sex with him. But when the
         professor puts on a condom, the carnivorous condom bites
         off his penis and disappears. Detective Mackaroni who
         gets the case thinks that the college girl just bit off
         her teacher's penis! Mackaroni goes to the motel himself
         to check out the crime scene, in the lobby he finds a
         gigolo named Bill and he asks him to follow him to
         crime room, there the two men attempt to have sex when
         they are suddenly interrupted by the attack of a killer
         condom.


